# Team Lead Agent - Minimal Configuration
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPORTANT: When team-lead runs as a per-task container (the normal mode),
# ALL values below are injected by the Launcher from registry-config.json
# (the "env" and "passThroughEnv" sections) and do NOT need to be set here.
#
# This file is only needed when running team-lead STANDALONE (e.g., for
# local debugging outside Docker).  In that case, uncomment and fill in
# the values you need.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# [OPTIONAL] LLM endpoint
#   Leave unset to use runtime-aware defaults:
#   - standalone local debug: http://localhost:1288/v1
#   - Docker container: http://host.docker.internal:1288/v1
#   - Rancher container: http://host.rancher-desktop.internal:1288/v1
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=

# [OPTIONAL] Agentic runtime backend
#   Default for per-task execution: copilot-cli
#   Other supported values: claude-code | copilot-connect | mock
# AGENT_RUNTIME=copilot-cli

# [OPTIONAL] Runtime model override (higher priority than OPENAI_MODEL)
# AGENT_MODEL=gpt-5-mini

# [OPTIONAL] Model name
#   Default: gpt-5-mini
#   Injected automatically in per-task mode via registry-config.json → env.OPENAI_MODEL
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5-mini

# [OPTIONAL] API key (leave blank if the LLM endpoint does not require one)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# [OPTIONAL] Allow mock fallback — for offline/test environments ONLY. Keep disabled in dev and prod.
#   Injected automatically in per-task mode via registry-config.json → env.ALLOW_MOCK_FALLBACK
ALLOW_MOCK_FALLBACK=0

# [OPTIONAL] GitHub PAT for Copilot CLI LLM tier (only if using CLI mode)
#   Set this in compass/.env instead — Compass injects it automatically
#   via passThroughEnv when launching this container.
# COPILOT_GITHUB_TOKEN=<your-copilot-github-token>
